hat info, pls enlighten us.[/quote]\n@Haier, I have already posted about this low quality supplier ...the decoys which he says as imported are NOT imported, they are same cheap made local stuff. He has only painted shiny paint on them (Shovelers only till now) and is trying to dodge people by saying they are Chinese & etc etc. The decoys have to have matte finish and durable paint (pref accurate paint too) alongwith rugged plastic used. He is saving on plastic and paint which wears off after 3 or 4 uses. At first sight, though it looks ok. You can try your luck.', 0, 1, '110.36.14.146', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 5415, 172265),
