(158165, 4545, 157841, 'AK47', 162, '', 1289300082, 'Warranty on guns is just as normal as warranty on a DVD player.\n\nThe problem is that we do not get warranty on guns in Pakistan, due to one factor only:\n\nOur importers do not ask for warranty on the guns from the manufacturers, hence they get the items below standard prices, i.e a $500 gun that includes a warranty, would be available at say $350 or so without warranty, so when we compare our prices in Pakistan as being lower for the same guns as in the states, etc, one factor is that our''s have not been charged with an accompanying warranty. It''s that simple.  ;)', 0, 1, '119.154.45.107', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 6437, 179376);
